data.text:
++Intro++

Welcome to Strong, The Official Fanlisting for the Character of Nora Hanen Gannon Buchanan on the ABC Soap Opera One Life To Live. For Appoximately 13 and 1/2 years, she has been played by the Amazing actress that is Hillary B Smith.

If you are a fan of Nora then feel free to join this fanlisting. It has Been approved by the FanListings at http://www.thefanlistings.org

++Updates++

++ March 31, 2006++

This Fan Listing was Launched

++ Rules ++

++ You MUST Be a fan of Nora's. Absolutely No exceptions. I don't want to find out that there's been people joing that hate her. ++

++ Please give me a Valid Email Address. I may have to contact you from time to time and it would be easier if I knew your correct address. Thanks.++

++ Please give me the name of the country you live in. You don't have to be really specific but I need to know if you are from CA, CAN, etc. ++

++ Give me your real first name. I'm not interested in last names as everyone is entitled to their privacy. But I don't want no code names or internet screen names. Just a simple name is fine. ++

++ you do NOT have to have a website to join but if you do then all I ask is that you grab one of the codes and link me. Thanks.++

++ To be sure you are truly a Nora Fan, I am asking you to tell me your favoriate Nora Moment.

++Member List Last Updadted on March , 31, 2006++
